---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout 
  title="About Us | Shining Road Technology — Pavement Maintenance Solutions"
  description="Shenyang Shining Road Technology — manufacturer of asphalt crack sealing, cold mix asphalt, and pavement preservation products. Technology licensing and production plants available."
>
  <section class="py-16">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
      <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold mb-3">About Us</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-500 mb-12">Shenyang Shining Road Technology Co., Ltd.</p>

      <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
        <p class="lead text-xl text-gray-700">
          We are a professional manufacturer and technology provider specializing in pavement maintenance products — 
          from crack sealants and cold mix asphalt to complete production plants and technology licensing. 
          Headquartered in Shenyang, Liaoning Province, China, we serve contractors, distributors, and manufacturers 
          in over 30 countries.
        </p>

        <h2>What We Do</h2>
        <p>
          Our core business spans three pillars:
        </p>
        <ol>
          <li><strong>Product Manufacturing</strong> — Hot-applied crack sealants, cold pour fillers, self-adhesive tapes, 
          cold mix asphalt, emulsified asphalt, and pavement sealcoats. Every product is tested to international standards 
          (ASTM, AASHTO, EN) with Certificate of Analysis provided on every shipment.</li>
          <li><strong>Plant & Equipment</strong> — Turnkey cold mix asphalt production plants from 5 to 30 TPH. 
          Complete solution including mixer, dryer, bagging line, dust collection, and PLC automation. 
          Factory acceptance testing, on-site installation, and operator training included.</li>
          <li><strong>Technology Licensing</strong> — Full technology transfer for cold mix asphalt manufacturing. 
          Proprietary formulas, raw material sourcing network, QC laboratory setup, operator training, 
          and ongoing R&D support. Launch your own branded product line in 90 days.</li>
        </ol>

        <h2>Our Philosophy</h2>
        <p>
          Pavement maintenance is one of the highest-ROI investments in infrastructure. 
          Spending $1 on crack sealing today saves $5–10 in rehabilitation costs 5 years later. 
          Our mission is to make high-quality maintenance materials accessible to every market — 
          not just through product supply, but through technology transfer that enables local production.
        </p>

        <h2>Quality Commitment</h2>
        <p>
          Every batch undergoes in-house laboratory testing before release. 
          Our quality control covers:
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Raw material inspection</strong> — Incoming aggregates, bitumen, polymers, and additives</li>
          <li><strong>In-process testing</strong> — Temperature, mixing time, gradation during production</li>
          <li><strong>Finished product certification</strong> — Full ASTM/AASHTO test suite per product specification</li>
          <li><strong>Retained samples</strong> — 12-month sample retention for traceability</li>
          <li><strong>Third-party verification</strong> — Annual independent lab testing for key products</li>
        </ul>

        <h2>Global Presence</h2>
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6 not-prose my-8">
          <div class="bg-blue-50 rounded-xl p-6">
            <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-primary mb-1">30+</div>
            <div class="text-gray-600">Countries served</div>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-amber-50 rounded-xl p-6">
            <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-amber-600 mb-1">50+</div>
            <div class="text-gray-600">Active distributor partners</div>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-green-50 rounded-xl p-6">
            <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-green-600 mb-1">5+</div>
            <div class="text-gray-600">Production plants delivered</div>
          </div>
          <div class="bg-purple-50 rounded-xl p-6">
            <div class="text-3xl font-bold text-purple-600 mb-1">10+</div>
            <div class="text-gray-600">Technology licensing partners</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <h2>Our Team</h2>
        <p>
          Our team includes materials engineers, chemical formulation specialists, mechanical engineers, 
          and international trade professionals. We maintain ongoing collaboration with research institutions 
          for continuous product improvement and new formulation development.
        </p>

        <div class="not-prose mt-12 text-center bg-gray-50 rounded-2xl p-10">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">Interested in Working With Us?</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600 mb-6 max-w-md mx-auto">
            Whether you're a distributor, contractor, or manufacturer — we'd love to discuss how we can support your business.
          </p>
          <div class="flex justify-center gap-4">
            <a href="/contact/" class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 bg-primary text-white font-semibold rounded-lg hover:bg-blue-700 transition-colors">
              Contact Us
            </a>
            <a href="/products/" class="inline-flex items-center px-6 py-3 border-2 border-primary text-primary font-semibold rounded-lg hover:bg-primary hover:text-white transition-colors">
              Browse Products
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
